data.description: 4 Bedroom / 2 Bath on 1.05 acres just outside of the town of St. Maries. Treed privacy with gorgeous views from the wrap around deck. Walkout basement with sliding glass doors ideal for entertaining!! Paved from the highway to the house. Detached one car garage. Open yard on the back with .56 acres of trees below the home. Enjoy gardening on the right of the house with apple trees! Gorgeous trees surrounding the home secluding it. Don't miss out on this home!!
